<taxonomicName id="4C3A4D685B725006FC9BFBE335E25A44" box="[792,978,1120,1141]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Loxandrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="148" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis id="B94EEAF95B725006FC9BFBE3354E5A44" box="[792,894,1120,1141]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="148">Loxandrus</emphasis>
species.
</taxonomicName>
The males and females can usually be identified by using external characters.’’
